trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator" /> class provides enumeration functionality for the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: A classe <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator" /> fornece funcionalidade de enumeração para a coleção <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.Current" /> property retrieves the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object from the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.Current" /> recupera o objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> atual da coleção <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object that represents the current recipient in the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> objeto que representa o destinatário atual no <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> coleção.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.MoveNext" /> method advances the enumeration to the next <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object in the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.MoveNext" /> avança a enumeração para o próximo objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> na coleção <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: <see langword="true" /> if the enumeration successfully moved to the next <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object; <see langword="false" /> if the enumeration moved past the last item in the enumeration.
trans-unit.target: <see langword="true" /> se a enumeração foi movida com êxito para o próximo objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" />, <see langword="false" /> se a enumeração foi movida para frente do último item na enumeração.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="M:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.Reset" /> method resets the enumeration to the first <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object in the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: O método <see cref="M:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.Reset" /> redefine a enumeração para o primeiro objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> na coleção <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.System#Collections#IEnumerator#Current" /> property retrieves the current <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object from the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: A propriedade <see cref="P:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientEnumerator.System#Collections#IEnumerator#Current" /> recupera o objeto <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> atual da coleção <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> object that represents the current recipient in the <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> collection.
trans-unit.target: Um <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipient" /> objeto que representa o destinatário atual no <see cref="T:System.Security.Cryptography.Pkcs.CmsRecipientCollection" /> coleção.
